TITLE: Creating an OpenAPI Route
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create an OpenAPI route using the createRoute function, specifying method, path, request params, and response schema.
SOURCE: https://github.com/honojs/middleware/blob/main/packages/zod-openapi/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
