TITLE: Complete Google OAuth Setup with Hono
DESCRIPTION: A full example of setting up Google OAuth in a Hono application, including importing necessary modules and configuring the middleware.
SOURCE: https://github.com/honojs/middleware/blob/main/packages/oauth-providers/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
